## Tamil AI Project தொடர்பு | Relevance to Tamil AI Project {#தொடர்பு}

### Phase-wise Utility | படப்படி பயன்பாடு

| Project Phase | How Purananuru Helps |
|--------------|---------------------|
| **Phase 1 — Data Collection** | 400 poems = structured classical Tamil training data |
| **Phase 2 — Transliteration** | Sangam Tamil script to Roman/modern Tamil mapping |
| **Phase 3 — Dictionary** | Rich source of rare Sangam-era vocabulary and grammar |
| **Phase 4 — Verse Translation** | English translations by Hart & Ramanujan = translation pairs |
